ions in general, while Lee Hock Guan examines changes in the voting pattern in the Klang Valley.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aElectionszMalaysiaxHistoryy21st century. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Essays.2bisacsh1 aBeng, Ooi Kee, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGuan, Lee Hock, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHock Guan, Lee, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKesavapany, K., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSaravanamuttu, Johan, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aSaravanamuttu, Johan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertISEAS Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2015z978311066300608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertISEAS eBook Package Backlist 2000-2014z978311060668340uhttps://doi.org/10.1355/978981230897940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789812308979423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9789812308979.jpg  a978-3-11-060668-3  ISEAS eBook Package Backlist 2000-2014c2000d2014  a978-3-11-066300-6  ISEAS Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2015c2000d2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK